### ğŸ” **Quick Comparison**

| Feature          | On-Chain               | Off-Chain              |
| ---------------- | ---------------------- | ---------------------- |
| **Location**     | Blockchain network     | Outside the blockchain |
| **Cost**         | High (due to gas fees) | Low or free            |
